Note: 2X’s the flow trigger setting.  In pressure trigger, its fixed at 1 LPM.  With Intellisync option its 4LPM.  If flow trigger setting is Less than 2LPM, then base flow =4L/min Pressure trigger: 1 l/min

The bias flow of the Life200 ventilator is up to 40 LPM coming out of the vent, based on volume and I-Time settings, but that is PRIOR to entrainment from the POV (proportional open ventilation) venturi ports.
When you factor in the entrainment flow, based on volume and I-Time settings, the total delivered flow can be up to 120 LPM.
